name: Realistic light bulb icon/写实灯泡图标
description:
This is an icon exercise work, thank you for watching.

There is currently an interaction bug in this work. When the light bulb moves, it will leave a shadow of the frame. If you know the solution, I hope you can help me solve it.

这是一份图标练习作品，谢谢观赏。

目前这个作品中有一个交互方面的BUG，当灯泡移动时，会留下一个frame的影子，如果你知道解决办法，希望你能帮助我解决它。
